      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous preservation. The exterior is finished in a deep, mirror-like gloss, completely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks, and has been protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a 'time capsule'\u2014the premium leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, the carpets are pristine under original mats, and the interior still carries that distinct factory aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions with out-of-the-box precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy. It includes a comprehensive binder of service history, all original keys, and the window sticker. This is an investment-grade specimen destined for a serious enthusiast who demands the absolute best.",
